{
  "stem": "23428.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And in many ways, this job, the way I think it was, was that of the-- of the [INAUDIBLE] in the courts of the Austrian Emperors, the guys who were responsible for the financial well-beings of the-- of the entire thing.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so he was and he was very successful at it, at, I think, bringing this economic monster to fruition, to life, so much so that to the present day the Prince Hohenlohe administration sends my mother a small check every month in appreciation of what my father did for them.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that went well until 1936, when he had to leave the country.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Apparently he was forewarned of an arrest at that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'36.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'36.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm '27.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was when I was-- when I was 9 years old.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nine years old he left the family-- and we were living in Berlin at that time-- and went to Belgium and to-- ultimately to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Four years.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we-- OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Undoubtedly what prompted us to move away was the end of the bank career of my father's and the beginning of his career with the Hohenlohes, because the place where we moved to, Slawentzitz, was the main castle of Prince Hohenlohe and the seat of much of his administration.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we only stayed there for one year.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was memorable for me only because I started school, primary school,",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Slawentzitz.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "S-L-A-W-E-N-T-Z-I-T-Z, in Upper Silesia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not really.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My memories are mostly associated with a place we moved then, after one year in Slawentzitz, which was Berlin, where I went to primary school and started high school.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
